data.title: What is the ‘CW’?
data.meta_description:
Answer (1 of 7): The CW is a television network known for airing both superhero action series (The Arrow-verse, including Supergirl, Arrow, The Flash, Legends of Tomorrow) and sexy teen-drama shows (Vampire Diaries, Riverdale) as well as the huge hit Supernatural.
